-- Healthscope May Make Acquisition by End of Month, Financial Review Says
-- B y   B e n   S h a r p l e s
-- 2010-11-09T20:31:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/healthscope-may-make-acquisition-by-end-of-month-financial-review-says.html
     Nov. 10 (Bloomberg) --Healthscope Ltd. may make its first
acquisition under the leadership of Rob Cooke by the end of this
month, the Australian Financial Review reported, citing analysts
it didn’t identify  The company may purchase the pathology unit of
Healthbridge, the Review said, citing the unidentified analysts.
The next logical acquisition may be Primary Health Care’s
pathology assets, the newspaper said, citing people it didn’t
name.  To contact the reporter on this story:
